Comment: thadcollins said "Home is home. But "home" shouldn't just be a physical location, it should be a peace of mind. An enduring image. So this is my home. The corner I lived on for the first 23 years of my life. I've seen so much happen on this corner, staring at these signs. It's a comfort zone, a security blanket.

So I'll take this image with me, back to my new home! And as I end 2014, I know that I've done this little block called home, proud! I got out and am doing something new and exciting in the world! And it's so awesome to know that I can move halfway across the world, but still reflect back and call this home.

Brooklyn; New York; America; Home: I love you! It's been so fun to be back for a few weeks! It'll be awhile, but I can't wait to come back home! Don't worry, I'll need no directions & no prodding!

I can't wait to show you what I'll accomplish in 2015!

#BrooklynDeferred"
